2.1.2 (2013-09-26)
==================
- fixed message list clicking and selecting
- fixed settings sections iframe size

2.1.1(2013-09-12)
=================
- upgraded the skin to be compatible with Roundcube 0.9.4

2.1 (2013-08-22)
================
- fixed icon display problems on browsers that don't support svg

2.0 (2013-05-30)
================
- made the skin compatible with Roundcube 0.9
- improved user interactivity
- improved the design
- improved icon rendering on high resolution devices
- improved border rendering on high resolution devices
- changed icon set to svg
- improved message list display
- added "drag down to refresh" function for the message list
- added recognision for tablet devices
- added folder sidebar on tablets
- added expanded top menu on tablets
- added bottom toolbar for selection actions on tablets
- made the skin compatible with the new rcs_mobile_switch and rcs_mobile_options plugins
- included thumbnail
- changed popup dialogs to full-screen overlays
- disabled tinymce (not working properly on mobile devices)
- added automatic loading of the default settings page
- redesigned action buttons and menus to improve user experience
- combined most images into sprites to maximize speed and minimize needed bandwidth

1.7.3 (2013-03-27)
==================
- hidden the skin preview section added by the settings plugin because the mobile preview is not supported by the plugin

1.7.2 (2013-02-26)
==================
- added functionality for expanding and collapsing mail subfolders

